<div class="wrap">
	<div class="grid_9 breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> \ <a href="/products">Products &amp; Services</a> \ Virtual Private Link </div>
	
	<div class="grid_9">
		<img src="/assets/gr_virtualprivatenetwork.jpg" alt="Virtual Private Network" width="700" height="190" style="padding-top:15px;">
		<h3>As a business, you probably use more than one technology platform for your networking purposes that can result in wasted resources and a complicated support system.  Our Layer 2 Ethernet solutions are ideal for companies looking for cost-effective, flexible, reliable and secure connections.  By leveraging a private path across the NTT Communications network, we offer direct connections both domestically and internationally. </h3>
	</div>
	
	<div class="grid_3">	
		<h4>VLink Services</h4>
        	<p>Our Layer 2 Virtual Private Network solutions are ideal for companies looking for direct connections between multiple locations. By leveraging our innovative IP infrastructure, we offer reliable and cost-effective point-to-point, point-to-multipoint, and multipoint-to-multipoint connections across our Global IP Network.
            <br />
			<br />
			<a href="vlink.cfm" >Learn More &raquo;</a></p>
	</div>
    <div class="grid_3">	
		<h4>Global Virtual Link Services</h4>
        	<p>Leverage the scope and reliability of the NTT Communications Tier-1 Global IP Network when making Ethernet connections between North America, Asia and Europe with Global Virtual Link. Global Virtual Link is a Layer 2 Virtual Private Network solution that enables a seamless connection between two locations offering a secure and flexible alternative to costly private lines.
            <br />
			<br />
			<a href="global-virtual-link.cfm" >Learn More &raquo;</a></p>
	</div>
		
	
	
